choices.text:
by the MODICA, a minibus crossing two cities. Getting there later than 6:30 p.m. is already complicated since they are not usually not standing but in a row and the last Km are walking…..back home I try to convince myself to walk one block, enough to lose the car in the garage.

What’s Good For You? A Natural Substance that Suppresses White Sugar Cravings

How many do you remember the times when, while looking at food labels looking for ingredients you recognize, reading food labels has started to feel like crossing the Amazon River? Natural sugar is your demon ……Sugar is a fact of life and it does your health justice … to understand the good ……

“Do all the good you can,

By all the means you can.

In all the ways you can.

In all the places you can.

At all the times you can.

To all the people you can.

As long as ever you can.” John Wesley

Always Heard This Bubble Story? Then I worry about you!

Many of my friends will tell you I`m obsessed with public transportation! Reading and knowing the price of a lift, using less sugar, making tea and coffee at home, staying late to watch the moon with jellyfish in the middle of the ocean, biking around the island, watching for close gluten-free restaurants and beside ALL that … always learning more and posting on:
